 <span data-ttu-id="ffe48-102"><xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>类可以强制使用架构或文档类型定义 (DTD) 验证。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffe48-102">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> class can enforce validation using a schema or document type definition (DTD).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ffe48-103"><xref:System.Xml.ValidationType>枚举指定的所创建的验证类型<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>实例应执行。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffe48-103">The <xref:System.Xml.ValidationType> enumeration specifies the type of validation the created <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance should perform.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ffe48-104"><xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>实例可以是任一验证<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>对象创建的<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A>方法，或<xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffe48-104">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance can be either a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> object created by the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method, or an <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ffe48-105">验证模型具有三个特征，严格、 带有提示性，以及状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffe48-105">The validation model has three characteristics, strict, informative, and status.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ffe48-106">Strict，不允许混合验证类型，信息性提供了一条警告，如果找不到架构或文档类型定义 (DTD)，并且状态提供了警告，如果不能为元素和属性架构中的执行验证。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffe48-106">Strict, does not allow the mixing of validation types, informative provides a warning if the schema or document type definition (DTD) cannot be found, and status provides warnings if validation cannot be performed for elements and attributes from schemas.</span></span>  
  
